OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FReport into BBC chairman's 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fappointment 'imminent'     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A report examining the appointment of  
OL,6, the BBC's chairman Richard Sharp is    
OL,7, expected imminently.                   
OL,9,FAdam Heppinstall KC has examined       
OL,10,Fwhether the appointment was in line    
OL,11,Fwith the government's Governance Code  
OL,12,Ffor Public Appointments.               
OL,14,FIt follows questions raised about Mr   
OL,15,FSharp's role in securing a loan for the
OL,16,Fthen Prime Minister Boris Johnson.     
OL,18,FWhile there has not been official      
OL,19,Fconfirmation, sources say the report   
OL,20,Fcould be published on Friday.          
